  <brief_title>Lycopene Following Aneurysmal Subarachnoid Haemorrhage</brief_title>
  <acronym>LASH</acronym>
  <official_title>Acute Oral Lycopene Therapy on Cerebral Autoregulation and Delayed Ischaemic Deficits Following Aneurysmal Subarachnoid Haemorrhage (LASH): A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
